                                        <fixVersion>1.0.0</fixVersion>
                                        <due></due>
                            <votes>0</votes>
                                    <watches>0</watches>
                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13100680" author="jbellis" created="Thu, 8 Sep 2011 20:46:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;what liveRatio was it logging on the OOM run?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13100707" author="brandon.williams" created="Thu, 8 Sep 2011 21:22:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a system.log with your extra debug statements and Memtable set to DEBUG.  It OOM&apos;d many times, but never actually dumped.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13101198" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 9 Sep 2011 13:26:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;What is happening is, the slab-allocated row keys are being put into the IndexSummary of the new sstable on flush.  So the regions can only be GC&apos;s post-compaction.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13101230" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 9 Sep 2011 14:17:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;v2 re-clones into indexposition instead of trying to avoid cloning at all.  this should be a small penalty since we&apos;re only re-cloning sampled keys, not all of them.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13101347" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 9 Sep 2011 17:18:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;v3 also applies getMinimalKey to SSTR.first, last fields.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13101387" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 9 Sep 2011 18:01:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;v4 fixes NPE on sstable load&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13101406" author="brandon.williams" created="Fri, 9 Sep 2011 18:09:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13101413" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 9 Sep 2011 18:13:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
